{"tid":801302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅雨下高鐵車廠變水城！浸壞轉軌器 列車冇法改道","createTime":"2018-08-31T13:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T10:30:27.000Z","uid":41404,"like":202,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":112,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfd89ce533d69fa857a8e86abd91749dce4d9c3","tid":801302,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:47:28.000Z","msg":"日前紅雨襲港，高鐵香港段的石崗車廠被洪水倒灌。立法會議員譚文豪今日再取得一批車廠內部相片，可見部分路軌嚴重水浸。譚引述消息稱，該石崗路段負責轉換路軌的路軌轉轍器，在暴雨中被浸壞，要即時更換，他擔心若高鐵通車後，路軌轉轍器再次因下雨故障，如列車駛向錯誤方向，後果或不堪設想。<br />\n譚文豪指，從相片中可見，銀白色正方型的部件即為路軌轉轍器，部件內有電動摩打，可以操控路軌改道，據他所知，該路軌轉轍器在紅雨當日，因去水設計出問題被浸壞，令控制室無法控制列車改道。譚認為當日並非百年一遇的大豪雨，但高鐵設計竟然連紅雨考驗都無法通過，明顯是重大缺失，港鐵仍辯稱事件不影響高鐵通車日期。他促港鐵交待在今次紅雨下，車廠共有多少部件損壞及涉的維修費。<br />\n《蘋果》亦接獲消息人士舉報，指紅雨當日車廠內有多處水浸，包括主大樓消防泵房，水深達一呎以上；車輪檢測器在水浸後完全失靈，暫不能監測車輪狀況；有蓋維修車庫有軌道如「河流」般嚴重水浸；控制中心有電子儀器房嚴重滲水；但車廠內沙包嚴重不足，即使手動抽水泵亦只有數個，根本不足以應付豪雨。從讀者提供的相片可見，一段路軌嚴重水浸，流水湧入路軌中央，另一處疑似機房位置，亦嚴重水浸。《蘋果》向港鐵查詢，但暫未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180831/58631073\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58631073&d=wlg5qpysbMwI8blMwSHqzUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=d93de033\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58631073&h=462f3c81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180831/58631073</a>"},{"pid":"c7362325faa697d89d13c44e2fcd0eccdfdc7585","tid":801302,"uid":41404,"like":132,"dislike":1,"score":131,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535720309_55d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535720309_55d0.jpg&h=227766b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535720309_728c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535720309_728c.jpg&h=d708824b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca394689ac429591bdfebfbc47c694a52b99f034","tid":801302,"uid":52946,"like":164,"dislike":0,"score":164,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:48:51.000Z","msg":"千億工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"241472de59bca81d4281983d4c2951a0f1cae5eb","tid":801302,"uid":41404,"like":175,"dislike":0,"score":175,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535720362_6576.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535720362_6576.jpg&h=292e8094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚文豪指，高鐵路軌的去水設計，竟連紅色暴雨的考驗都無法通過，明顯是重大缺失。譚文豪提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535720362_9ba2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535720362_9ba2.jpg&h=641cdf65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銀白色正方型為高鐵列車轉軌器，內有電動摩打，可操控列車改道，疑因去水設計缺憾，日前被浸壞，令控制室無法控制列車改道。譚文豪提供圖片"},{"pid":"d1def9e5710e44aa88064e896bd3cd0a8e8bcbc0","tid":801302,"uid":73915,"like":208,"dislike":1,"score":207,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:49:24.000Z","msg":"東方威尼斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又亮劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"384fa7b277c729cc925b43a2e3eb3c38b32bd6e9","tid":801302,"uid":22913,"like":115,"dislike":0,"score":115,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"水為財啊<br />\n維修又賺一筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b694c11d922c4c11b849189a59eee2369384df","tid":801302,"uid":10680,"lik